title: Morning Show
subtitle: Getting up with someone who cares. Dein unterhaltsamer Start in den Tag mit Gästen, Spielen, Comedy, aktuellen Themen und News in Englisch und Deutsch.
description:
The FM4 Morning Show with Hal Rock and Lena Raffetseder
We're Santas little helpers today, waking you up in style on this Heiligabend! All day we'll fulfill your song requests in support of the initiative "Mental Health Days". And we're opening the final door of the FM4 Ticketadventkalender: It's tickets to the FM4 Geburtstagsfest in January! Join us and enjoy holiday cheer by Hal Rock and Lena Raffetseder!
